    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Factoriant》是一款建造类游戏，玩家将建立一个由蚂蚁全面运营的庞大地下工厂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一只年轻的蚁后。挖掘隧道、搬运食物、孵化工蚁，并实现蚁群生产的自动化。<br>打造一个庞大的地下工厂，成千上万只蚂蚁日夜不停地工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘巢穴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/ae758df041cdaeb4d79b8daef9356f0b.poster.avif?t=1761053641\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/ae758df041cdaeb4d79b8daef9356f0b.webm?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/ae758df041cdaeb4d79b8daef9356f0b.mp4?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的地下工厂需要足够的空间。<br>合理规划隧道，优化物流，划分生产区域，并抵御外敌入侵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全面自动化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/58f572993b5dc7672af696266798e959.poster.avif?t=1761053641\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/58f572993b5dc7672af696266798e959.webm?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/58f572993b5dc7672af696266798e959.mp4?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有工作都可以实现自动化。<br>蚂蚁会排队运输食物和材料，组装产品，研究新技术等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着蚁群的发展，甚至飞行的蜜蜂和奔跑在轨道上的陆龟也会加入你的工业帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索与工业化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向更深处挖掘，发现矿石、石油等资源。<br>铺设管道，让你的蚁巢实现完全工业化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果敢于入侵人类的住宅，或许还能掌握天然气与电力等强大的能源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天敌来袭</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/3a486407d43aa14e19eeb98d30fa5f3b.poster.avif?t=1761053641\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/3a486407d43aa14e19eeb98d30fa5f3b.webm?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/3a486407d43aa14e19eeb98d30fa5f3b.mp4?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >饥饿的鸟类会捕食你的工蚁。<br>好奇的人类小孩甚至会为了好玩而淹没你的隧道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但你并非普通的蚂蚁——武装自己，奋起反击吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实的动物行为</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/393d0189599c0c72d77740cb3cbb253d.poster.avif?t=1761053641\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/393d0189599c0c72d77740cb3cbb253d.webm?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332860/extras/393d0189599c0c72d77740cb3cbb253d.mp4?t=1761053641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管游戏进行了趣味化处理，但许多设定灵感来源于真实生态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验切叶蚁的农业行为、扭颈鸟的捕食方式，以及与蚁球菌等共生生物之间迷人的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作模式：计划支持在线多人联机。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >载具与轨道：在地上与地下建造交通网络，快速运输远处资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放世界：无缝生成的地图让每一次探索都充满新鲜感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
